---
/** ServicesGrid.astro — Resumen de servicios para el home */
---

<section class="services section">
  <div class="services__container container">
    <header class="services__header section-header section-header--centered">
      <h2 class="services__eyebrow eyebrow">Nuestros Servicios</h2>
      <p class="services__title h2">Todo lo que necesitas para crecer en USA</p>
      <p class="section-header__desc">
        Desde tu sitio web hasta tus campañas publicitarias, somos tu equipo de marketing digital integral.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="services__grid">
      <article class="services__card card">
        <div class="services__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="services__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Web as a Service</h3>
        <p class="services__card-title h3">WaaS — Sistema de leads 24/7</p>
        <p class="services__card-body">
          Sitio web de alto rendimiento + CRM + Chatbot. Todo incluido desde $270/mes. Genera leads mientras duermes.
        </p>
        <a class="services__card-link" href="/servicios/waas">
          Ver WaaS →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="services__card card services__card--featured">
        <div class="services__card-badge badge">Más popular</div>
        <div class="services__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="services__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Diseño Web Premium</h3>
        <p class="services__card-title h3">Sitios a medida desde $4,000</p>
        <p class="services__card-body">
          Proyectos web corporativos completos. Propiedad total desde el día uno. WordPress o Astro con arquitectura SEO.
        </p>
        <a class="services__card-link" href="/servicios/diseno-web">
          Ver diseño web →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="services__card card">
        <div class="services__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="services__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Google Ads</h3>
        <p class="services__card-title h3">Búsquedas de alta intención</p>
        <p class="services__card-body">
          Setup $390 + gestión desde $290/mes. Campañas de long tail con estrategia de negativos para maximizar conversión.
        </p>
        <a class="services__card-link" href="/servicios/google-ads">
          Ver Google Ads →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="services__card card">
        <div class="services__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="services__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Meta Ads</h3>
        <p class="services__card-title h3">Facebook + Instagram Ads</p>
        <p class="services__card-body">
          Desde $490/mes. Incluye diseño de gráficas. Campañas con segmentación precisa del público latino en USA.
        </p>
        <a class="services__card-link" href="/servicios/meta-ads">
          Ver Meta Ads →
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="services__card card">
        <div class="services__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.27h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="services__card-eyebrow eyebrow">Redes Sociales</h3>
        <p class="services__card-title h3">Contenido orgánico con propósito</p>
        <p class="services__card-body">
          Desde $490/mes. Creación de gráficas y contenido. Estrategia orientada a construir autoridad y confianza.
        </p>
        <a class="services__card-link" href="/servicios/redes-sociales">
          Ver redes →
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- CTA card -->
      <article class="services__card services__card--cta">
        <p class="services__cta-title h3">¿No sabes cuál es el mejor para ti?</p>
        <p class="services__cta-body">Agenda una videollamada gratuita de 30 minutos y lo determinamos juntos.</p>
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contacto">Agenda gratis →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services__container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-space-xl);
  }

  .services__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;

    :has(> &) { container-type: inline-size; }

    @container (inline-size < 60rem) {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    @container (inline-size < 38rem) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .services__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .services__card--featured {
    border-color: rgba(56,178,240,0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56,178,240,0.06) 0%, rgba(103,197,135,0.06) 100%);
  }

  .services__card-icon {
    inline-size: 3rem;
    block-size: 3rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-m);
    background: var(--color-primary-ultra-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,178,240,0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .services__card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    inset-block-start: 1.5rem;
    inset-inline-end: 1.5rem;
  }

  .services__card-body {
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .services__card-link {
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-heading);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap var(--transition-fast);

    &:hover { color: var(--color-primary-light); }
  }

  .services__card--cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--gradient-brand-subtle);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(56,178,240,0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-l);
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .services__cta-body {
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
